{
  "stem": "8892.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so he went and privately paid a teacher who taught me all summer.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And sure enough, I had to learn geometry, arithmetic, German, and some other subject.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I studied all summer.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Oh, I wanted to be the best.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And when we went to-- when my father took me in, which was a town where they had a gymnasium, which is like university college.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They had the high school.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And of course you had to pay.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That was not supplied by government or anything.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And that's where the quota was that only three Jews can attend the school publicly between 100.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they didn't want to commute us too much.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They really cut.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And when I was cut down, and they said-- after, you know, the test and everything-- and sure enough, they wanted to just cut you down from mainly German.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I'll never forget.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And they said, sorry, I was in the first grade.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I didn't have all A's, and I wasn't good enough, and commuters they not take.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Well, I went home with my father just crying on the train, and I was just heart broken.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So that's why, when they didn't know what to do with me, so for that winter they let me go to my grandfather, because I was heart broken.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "That was my biggest thing in my life.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I wanted higher education.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They wouldn't-- they wouldn't let me feel it in-- as a smaller girl.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I had to sit through, like, you know, when they had their Catholic-- what they call it-- Catechism, OK, and they had their religious program or prayers, I would-- we Jewish girls, we would just sit.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there was not even a Jewish boy in our whole class, just the two girls.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We would just sit it through.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
